1
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:09,760
The Huang family, get out of Jiangyu City!

2
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,520
Get out of Jiangyu City!

3
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,600
The Huang family, get out of Jiangyu City!

4
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,640
Darn it, this You Tong is really awful!

5
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,040
All she does is stay out there all day

6
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,840
spreading rumors to mislead the public.

7
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:25,760
And the civilians actually believe her!

8
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:29,840
No, no.

9
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:31,400
We can't just sit back anymore.

10
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:32,920
We must arrest You Tong immediately,

11
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:34,200
so she won't be out there

12
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,320
spouting nonsense all day.

13
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:38,360
No.

14
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:39,920
If at this moment

15
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,040
we arrest her by force,

16
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,400
it will definitely make them think

17
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,000
we are feeling guilty.

18
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,720
They'll only get more agitated.

19
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:47,040
Jiangyu City's situation is already unstable.

20
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:48,920
If at this time we

21
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,040
completely turn the civilians against us,

22
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,440
then those uncles of mine

23
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:52,400
will definitely take advantage of it.

24
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:53,240
When that happens,

25
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,800
the entire Jiangyu City will fall into

26
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:56,120
a state of eternal doom.

27
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,960
I understand your difficulties too.

28
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:04,640
But we can't just

29
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,640
let this You Tong

30
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,760
do whatever she wants like this.

31
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,640
Of course we can't.

32
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,280
It's just that elite troops from all over

33
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,200
are gathered outside the city.

34
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:14,720
The civilians are panicking inside.

35
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,760
Only by letting them

36
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:18,000
vent their anger and calm down,

37
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:19,560
will we have a chance

38
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,200
to deal with this menace, You Tong.

39
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:27,040
The Huang family, get out of Jiangyu City!

40
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,560
I know

41
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:03,200
that when you were little, you really loved

42
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,280
the porridge Ba Gu made for you.

43
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:05,640
So I specially

44
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,000
asked her to make it for you.

45
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,000
Thank you.

46
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,240
Hurry and taste it.

47
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,960
It won't taste good if it gets cold.

48
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,400
Is it good?

49
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:33,720
It's good.

50
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,120
Then have some more.

51
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,720
Huang Jinrong!

52
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:52,600
What's wrong with you?

53
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,720
Don't scare me, Huang Jinrong.

54
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,720
Huang Jinrong, what's wrong?

55
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:57,960
Huang Jinrong!

56
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,840
Don't scare me.

57
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:00,840
What happened? What happened?

58
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:01,840
Chuncheng!

59
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:02,880
You're finally here.

60
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,080
Take a look at him, quick.

61
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:05,720
Inspector!

62
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,320
Inspector!

63
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,720
He's been poisoned.

64
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:11,440
What?

65
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,960
Good thing we found out in time.

66
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,800
The poisoning isn't severe.

67
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,120
How could he be poisoned?

68
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:24,440
Qingqing,

69
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,320
what did the Inspector eat today?

70
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:28,720
He ate the same things

71
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,000
as we did.

72
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:32,280
No.

73
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,560
Tonight he also had

74
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,560
the porridge made by Ba Gu.

75
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,080
Is there any of that porridge left?

76
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,600
Bring it to me.

77
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,080
I need to check it.

78
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:40,840
Okay.

79
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,000
This porridge has been poisoned.

80
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,400
As for what it is exactly,

81
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,560
I need to take it back to the station

82
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,120
and test it to find out.

83
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,600
The porridge is poisoned?

84
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,000
Yes.

85
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:58,840
Qingqing,

86
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,560
when you went to get the porridge,

87
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,720
did you see anyone?

88
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,280
I don't know.

89
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,840
Ba Gu gave me the porridge.

90
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,600
It's all my fault.

91
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,280
I shouldn't have trusted her so easily.

92
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,080
How can you blame yourself?

93
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:19,960
It's just that...

94
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,400
Ba Gu is an elder in the family.

95
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,960
She couldn't possibly poison me.

96
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:29,840
Darn it.

97
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:31,760
Young Master!

98
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:34,400
Young Master!

99
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,760
Ba Gu's daughter came

100
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,080
and said something happened to Ba Gu.

101
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,560
This is a scene deliberately faked by the killer

102
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:44,080
to confuse us.

103
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:45,520
Actually,

104
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:46,760
Ba Gu wasn't hanged to death,

105
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,320
but strangled.

106
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,320
Strangled by someone?

107
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:54,440
Yes.

108
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:55,960
For someone who dies by hanging,

109
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,840
their lips

110
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:57,400
and cheeks

111
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,280
would turn purplish-blue,

112
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,640
and livor mortis would be quite obvious.

113
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,640
But look,

114
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:01,640
on Ba Gu's face,

115
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,120
there are no such obvious signs.

116
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,640
Instead, on her neck,

117
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:06,080
there are marks of being strangled.

118
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,960
So I can conclude

119
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,440
that Ba Gu was strangled to death first

120
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:10,720
before being hung up.

121
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:21,880
They wanted to use Ba Gu's hands

122
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:23,760
to kill me,

123
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:25,640
and then disguised her death

124
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:27,960
as a suicide out of guilt.

125
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:56,840
You were poisoned tonight.

126
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,120
You need a good rest.

127
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,520
I'll take you back first.

128
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,440
Qingqing.

129
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:08,880
Ba Gu...

130
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,880
Ba Gu died because of me.

131
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:23,400
Ba Gu died because of me.

132
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,320
She died because of me.

133
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:42,200
This is not your fault.

134
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:46,520
We will definitely find the killer

135
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:50,640
and avenge Ba Gu

136
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,960
and your parents.

137
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:23,640
Uncle Yan

138
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:26,280
Xiaowu

139
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:27,760
Xiaowu has grown taller.

140
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,200
And stronger too.

141
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:31,520
Young Master.

142
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:32,200
Sit.

143
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:32,880
Please, sit down.

144
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:35,280
You little brat,

145
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:36,080
say hello.

146
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:37,840
Hello, mister.

147
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,640
Hello, miss.

148
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:40,960
Young Master,

149
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,320
you coming to see me so suddenly...

150
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,640
Is it about...

151
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:44,400
the Marshal?

152
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,080
Uncle Yan,

153
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,440
actually, I came here this time

154
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,440
just to ask you

155
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,640
about my father.

156
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,320
Did you find the killer?

157
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:54,080
No.

158
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:55,880
So please, for the sake of

159
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,080
your years of friendship with my father,

160
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,560
tell me about his early years.

161
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,720
Perhaps hidden within

162
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,200
are crucial clues

163
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,320
about the killer.

164
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,400
I don't really know much

165
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,520
about the Marshal's early years.

166
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:13,640
Uncle Yan,

167
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,080
you've known my father

168
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,640
for so many years.

169
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:16,880
You must know something.

170
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:18,320
Even if

171
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:19,880
it's just a tiny clue,

172
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,520
to me,

173
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:22,880
it is absolutely crucial.

174
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:24,760
Ever since a year ago,

175
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,520
when my mother died a tragic death...

176
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:27,400
This...

177
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,280
How could that be?

178
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,560
Didn't the Marshal say

179
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:30,400
that the First Wife

180
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,560
died of illness?

181
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:35,800
Because my mother's death

182
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,440
was truly too bizarre,

183
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,200
my father feared it would affect his reputation.

184
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,160
So he publicly claimed

185
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,480
that she died of illness.

186
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:43,720
He only conducted

187
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,840
a city-wide manhunt in secret.

188
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,080
The killer

189
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,560
went into hiding because of this,

190
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,720
leaving me with no way to investigate.

191
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:51,800
Because of this,

192
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,240
I had a huge fight with my father

193
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:55,920
and moved out

194
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,160
of the house.

195
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,440
Who knew that a year later,

196
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,360
this killer would appear once again

197
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,200
and kill my father,

198
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:04,600
my cousin,

199
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:05,840
and Ba Gu.

200
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:08,960
Uncle Yan,

201
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:11,160
we all understand the difficulties involved.

202
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:13,960
But if we don't uncover the truth,

203
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:15,560
Uncle Huang

204
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:16,440
won't be able to rest in peace.

205
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,200
You followed him for so long,

206
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,440
surely you wouldn't want

207
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,480
to see it end like this.

208
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:21,080
You...

209
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,200
Xiaowu,

210
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,840
go play in the yard for a while.

211
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:33,720
Okay.

212
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:43,840
There is indeed one thing

213
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,440
that the Marshal

214
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,320
never got over.
